# Explain AI 🤓

A simple AI-powered web app that explains any topic in an easy-to-understand way.

## 🚀 Features

- Enter any topic (e.g. Machine Learning, DBMS, etc.)
- Choose difficulty level
- Get simplified AI explanation
- Clean and minimal UI

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Python (Flask)
- HTML (Jinja templates)
- OpenRouter / OpenAI API
- dotenv (for API key security)

